{
  "texts": [
    "In adverse conditions, place recognition with a single-sensor or single-method could become challenging.",
    "Therefore, multimodal-based methods are also popular where the main idea is to combine 3D point clouds with other data (or sensor) modalities, such as RGB images, range images, and/or BEV information, etc.",
    "The combined multimodal data is then used as input for the subsequent place recognition processing.",
    "We divide multimodal-based methods into three categories: camera-LiDAR based, radar-LiDAR based, and multi-view fusion based methods.",
    "Camera-LiDAR based methods for 3D-PCPR mainly combine 3D point clouds with camera image information as input data for subsequent place recognition."
  ]
}